public class Car
extends Obstacle
The Car class provides a Car obstacle of varying colours in the Frogger game.

  • Constructor Details

    • Car

      public Car​(Car.CarTypes type, double xpos, double ypos, double speed)
      Creates a Car at the specified coordinates, sets it's speed, and displays the corresponding Image. If Images have not been loaded, load the images of all Car types into a static List.
      Parameters:
      type - Specifies the type of Car to instance.
      xpos - Specifies the x-coordinate. Measured in pixels.
      ypos - Specifies the y-coordinate. Measured in pixels.
      speed - Specifies the speed at which the instance should move across the screen. Measured in pixels per frame.
